    "macOS 15.1+ 支持将 App Store 应用安装到外部磁盘。\\n\\n请在 App Store → 设置中勾选「将大型 App 下载并安装到独立磁盘」，并选择当前外部驱动器。\\n\\n设置完成后点击「我已设置」，AppPorts 会自动创建 Applications 目录并检测管理这些应用。" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 15.1+ supports installing App Store apps to external disks.\\n\\nPlease go to App Store → Settings and check \"Download and install large apps to a separate disk\", then select your current external drive.\\n\\nAfter setup, click \"I've Set It Up\" and AppPorts will automatically create the Applications directory and detect these apps."
          }
        },
        "br" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "⠍⠁⠉⠠⠕⠠⠎ ⠼⠁⠼⠑⠲⠼⠁+ ⠎⠥⠏⠏⠕⠗⠞⠎ ⠊⠝⠎⠞⠁⠇⠇⠊⠝⠛ ⠠⠁⠏⠏ ⠠⠎⠞⠕⠗⠑ ⠁⠏⠏⠎ ⠞⠕ ⠑⠭⠞⠑⠗⠝⠁⠇ ⠙⠊⠎⠅⠎⠲\n\n⠠⠏⠇⠑⠁⠎⠑ ⠛⠕ ⠞⠕ ⠠⠁⠏⠏ ⠠⠎⠞⠕⠗⠑ → ⠠⠎⠑⠞⠞⠊⠝⠛⠎ ⠁⠝⠙ ⠉⠓⠑⠉⠅ \"⠠⠙⠕⠺⠝⠇⠕⠁⠙ ⠁⠝⠙ ⠊⠝⠎⠞⠁⠇⠇ ⠇⠁⠗⠛⠑ ⠁⠏⠏⠎ ⠞⠕ ⠁ ⠎⠑⠏⠁⠗⠁⠞⠑ ⠙⠊⠎⠅\"⠂ ⠞⠓⠑⠝ ⠎⠑⠇⠑⠉⠞ ⠽⠕⠥⠗ ⠉⠥⠗⠗⠑⠝⠞ ⠑⠭⠞⠑⠗⠝⠁⠇ ⠙⠗⠊⠧⠑⠲\n\n⠠⠁⠋⠞⠑⠗ ⠎⠑⠞⠥⠏⠂ ⠉⠇⠊⠉⠅ \"⠠⠊⠄⠧⠑ ⠠⠎⠑⠞ ⠠⠊⠞ ⠠⠥⠏\" ⠁⠝⠙ ⠠⠁⠏⠏⠠⠏⠕⠗⠞⠎ ⠺⠊⠇⠇ ⠁⠥⠞⠕⠍⠁⠞⠊⠉⠁⠇⠇⠽ ⠉⠗⠑⠁⠞⠑ ⠞⠓⠑ ⠠⠁⠏⠏⠇⠊⠉⠁⠞⠊⠕⠝⠎ ⠙⠊⠗⠑⠉⠞⠕⠗⠽ ⠁⠝⠙ ⠙⠑⠞⠑⠉⠞ ⠞⠓⠑⠎⠑ ⠁⠏⠏⠎⠲"
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 15.1+ supports installing App Store apps to external disks.\\n\\nPlease go to App Store → Settings and check \"Download and install large apps to a separate disk\", then select your current external drive.\\n\\nAfter setup, click \"I've Set It Up\" and AppPorts will automatically create the Applications directory and detect these apps."
          }
        },
