    "检测到「%@」已经是一个现有软链。\\n\\n软链路径：%@\\n目标路径：%@\\n\\n选择「规范化管理」后，AppPorts 会将这条软链接纳入受管状态，后续可直接还原。" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Detected that \"%1$@\" is already an existing symlink.\\n\\nSymlink path: %2$@\\nTarget path: %3$@\\n\\nAfter selecting \"Normalize management\", AppPorts will manage this symlink, allowing direct restoration later."
          }
        },
        "br" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "⠠⠙⠑⠞⠑⠉⠞⠑⠙ ⠞⠓⠁⠞ \"%1$@\" ⠊⠎ ⠁⠇⠗⠑⠁⠙⠽ ⠁⠝ ⠑⠭⠊⠎⠞⠊⠝⠛ ⠎⠽⠍⠇⠊⠝⠅⠲\n\n⠠⠎⠽⠍⠇⠊⠝⠅ ⠏⠁⠞⠓⠒ %2$@\n⠠⠞⠁⠗⠛⠑⠞ ⠏⠁⠞⠓⠒ %3$@\n\n⠠⠁⠋⠞⠑⠗ ⠎⠑⠇⠑⠉⠞⠊⠝⠛ \"⠠⠝⠕⠗⠍⠁⠇⠊⠵⠑ ⠍⠁⠝⠁⠛⠑⠍⠑⠝⠞\"⠂ ⠠⠁⠏⠏⠠⠏⠕⠗⠞⠎ ⠺⠊⠇⠇ ⠍⠁⠝⠁⠛⠑ ⠞⠓⠊⠎ ⠎⠽⠍⠇⠊⠝⠅⠂ ⠁⠇⠇⠕⠺⠊⠝⠛ ⠙⠊⠗⠑⠉⠞ ⠗⠑⠎⠞⠕⠗⠁⠞⠊⠕⠝ ⠇⠁⠞⠑⠗⠲"
