    "此应用位于外部磁盘的 Applications 目录，由 macOS 原生管理（macOS 15.1+ 功能）。App Store 可直接在此目录进行增量更新，无需通过 AppPorts 迁回。" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "yah alttatbiq yuwjad fi daleel Applications ealaa disk khariji, yudarah biashkalin asliyan min macOS (khassiyat macOS 15.1+). yumkin li-App Store eajla altaajirat alttarkibiyya biashkalin mubashir fi hadha aldaleel."
          }
        },
        "br" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "⠠⠞⠓⠊⠎ ⠁⠏⠏ ⠊⠎ ⠇⠕⠉⠁⠞⠑⠙ ⠊⠝ ⠞⠓⠑ ⠠⠁⠏⠏⠇⠊⠉⠁⠞⠊⠕⠝⠎ ⠙⠊⠗⠑⠉⠞⠕⠗⠽ ⠕⠝ ⠁⠝ ⠑⠭⠞⠑⠗⠝⠁⠇ ⠙⠊⠎⠅⠂ ⠍⠁⠝⠁⠛⠑⠙ ⠝⠁⠞⠊⠧⠑⠇⠽ ⠃⠽ ⠍⠁⠉⠠⠕⠠⠎ ⠐⠣⠍⠁⠉⠠⠕⠠⠎ ⠼⠁⠼⠑⠲⠼⠁+ ⠋⠑⠁⠞⠥⠗⠑⠐⠜⠲ ⠠⠁⠏⠏ ⠠⠎⠞⠕⠗⠑ ⠉⠁⠝ ⠏⠑⠗⠋⠕⠗⠍ ⠊⠝⠉⠗⠑⠍⠑⠝⠞⠁⠇ ⠥⠏⠙⠁⠞⠑⠎ ⠙⠊⠗⠑⠉⠞⠇⠽ ⠊⠝ ⠞⠓⠊⠎ ⠙⠊⠗⠑⠉⠞⠕⠗⠽ ⠺⠊⠞⠓⠕⠥⠞ ⠝⠑⠑⠙⠊⠝⠛ ⠞⠕ ⠍⠕⠧⠑ ⠃⠁⠉⠅ ⠧⠊⠁ ⠠⠁⠏⠏⠠⠏⠕⠗⠞⠎⠲"
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Diese App befindet sich im Applications-Verzeichnis auf einer externen Festplatte und wird nativ von macOS verwaltet (macOS 15.1+ Funktion). Der App Store kann in diesem Verzeichnis direkt inkrementelle Updates durchfuehren, ohne dass ein Ruecktransfer ueber AppPorts erforderlich ist."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This app is located in the Applications directory on an external disk, managed natively by macOS (macOS 15.1+ feature). App Store can perform incremental updates directly in this directory without needing to move back via AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "eo" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Chi tiu aplikacio troviighas en la Applications-direktoro sur ekstera disko, administrita de macOS (funkcio macOS 15.1+). App Store povas fari inkrementajn ghisdatighojn rekte en chi tiu direktoro, sen bezono reveni per AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Esta app se encuentra en el directorio Applications de un disco externo, administrada de forma nativa por macOS (funcion macOS 15.1+). App Store puede realizar actualizaciones incrementales directamente en este directorio, sin necesidad de volver mediante AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cette application se trouve dans le repertoire Applications sur un disque externe, geree nativement par macOS (fonctionnalite macOS 15.1+). L'App Store peut effectuer des mises a jour incrementales directement dans ce repertoire, sans necessiter de retour via AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "hi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "yah app baahaari disk par Applications drectory mein sthit hai, macOS dvaaraa mool roop se prabandhit (macOS 15.1+ suvidha). App Store is drectory mein seedha inkremental apdet kar sakta hai, AppPorts ke maadhyam se vaapas aane ki zaroorat nahin."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Aplikasi ini berada di direktori Applications pada disk eksternal, dikelola secara native oleh macOS (fitur macOS 15.1+). App Store dapat melakukan pembaruan inkremental langsung di direktori ini, tanpa perlu kembali melalui AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Questa app si trova nella directory Applications su un disco esterno, gestita nativamente da macOS (funzionalita macOS 15.1+). L'App Store puo eseguire aggiornamenti incrementali direttamente in questa directory, senza necessita di ritorno tramite AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This app is located in the Applications directory on an external disk, managed natively by macOS (macOS 15.1+ feature). App Store can perform incremental updates directly in this directory without needing to move back via AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이 앱은 외부 디스크의 Applications 디렉토리에 있으며 macOS가 네이티브로 관리합니다(macOS 15.1+ 기능). App Store는 이 디렉토리에서 직접 증분 업데이트를 수행할 수 있으므로 AppPorts를 통해 되돌릴 필요가 없습니다."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Deze app bevindt zich in de Applications-map op een externe schijf, beheerd door macOS (macOS 15.1+ functie). De App Store kan direct incrementele updates uitvoeren in deze map, zonder terugkeer via AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ta aplikacja znajduje sie w katalogu Applications na dysku zewnetrznym, zarzadzana natywnie przez macOS (funkcja macOS 15.1+). App Store moze wykonywac przyrostowe aktualizacje bezposrednio w tym katalogu, bez koniecznosci powrotu przez AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "pt" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Este app esta no diretorio Applications em um disco externo, gerenciado nativamente pelo macOS (funcao macOS 15.1+). A App Store pode realizar atualizacoes incrementais diretamente neste diretorio, sem necessidade de retorno pelo AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Eto prilozhenie nakhoditsya v direktorii Applications na vneshnem diske, upravlyayemaya nativno macOS (funktsiya macOS 15.1+). App Store mozhet vypolnyat inkrementalnyye obnovleniya neposredstvo v etoy direktorii, bez neobkhodimosti vozvrashcheniya cherez AppPorts."
          }
        },
        "th" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "app ni yang yu nai drectory Applications nai disk nork, chu kan duai macOS bang don thi (khunos macOS 15.1+). App Store ja kan abpdet pen incrementally tron der ni thing tong yai AppPorts"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bu uygulama harici diskin Applications dizininde bulunur ve macOS tarafindan yerel olarak yonetilir (macOS 15.1+ ozelligi). App Store bu dizinde dogrudan artirmali guncelleme yapabilir, AppPorts ile geri tasimaya gerek yoktur."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ung dung nay nam trong thu muc Applications tren dia ngoai, duoc quan ly boi macOS (tinh nang macOS 15.1+). App Store co the thuc hien cap nhat tang luong truc tiep trong thu muc nay, khong can di chuyen lai qua AppPorts."
