    "迁移完成。是否对已迁移的 %lld 个应用进行 Ad-hoc 重签名？\\n\\n重签名后应用可在本地正常启动，Finder「已损坏」提示将消失。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "اكتملت عملية النقل. هل تريد إعادة توقيع %lld تطبيقًا تم نقله بشكل Ad-hoc؟\n\nبعد التوقيع، يمكن تشغيل التطبيقات بشكل طبيعي وسيختفي تحذير Finder \"تالف\"."
          }
        },
        "br" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "⠠⠍⠊⠛⠗⠁⠞⠊⠕⠝ ⠉⠕⠍⠏⠇⠑⠞⠑⠲ ⠠⠺⠕⠥⠇⠙ ⠽⠕⠥ ⠇⠊⠅⠑ ⠞⠕ ⠠⠁⠙⠤⠓⠕⠉ ⠗⠑⠎⠊⠛⠝ ⠞⠓⠑ %lld ⠍⠊⠛⠗⠁⠞⠑⠙ ⠁⠏⠏⠎⠦\n\n⠠⠁⠋⠞⠑⠗ ⠗⠑⠎⠊⠛⠝⠊⠝⠛⠂ ⠁⠏⠏⠎ ⠉⠁⠝ ⠇⠁⠥⠝⠉⠓ ⠝⠕⠗⠍⠁⠇⠇⠽ ⠁⠝⠙ ⠞⠓⠑ ⠠⠋⠊⠝⠙⠑⠗ \"⠙⠁⠍⠁⠛⠑⠙\" ⠺⠁⠗⠝⠊⠝⠛ ⠺⠊⠇⠇ ⠙⠊⠎⠁⠏⠏⠑⠁⠗⠲"
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migration abgeschlossen. Möchten Sie die %lld migrierten Apps Ad-hoc neu signieren?\n\nNach dem Signieren können Apps normal gestartet werden und die Finder-Warnung \"beschädigt\" verschwindet."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migration complete. Would you like to Ad-hoc resign the %lld migrated apps?\n\nAfter resigning, apps can launch normally and the Finder \"damaged\" warning will disappear."
          }
        },
        "eo" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migrado kompleta. Ĉu vi volas resubskribi la %lld migritajn aplikaĵojn Ad-hoc?\n\nPost subskribo, aplikaĵoj povas normale lanĉi kaj la Finder-a averto \"difektita\" malaperos."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migración completada. ¿Desea firmar las %lld apps migradas en Ad-hoc?\n\nDespués de firmar, las apps pueden iniciarse normalmente y la advertencia \"dañado\" de Finder desaparecerá."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migration terminée. Voulez-vous resigner les %lld apps migrées en Ad-hoc ?\n\nAprès la signature, les apps peuvent se lancer normalement et l'avertissement \"endommagé\" du Finder disparaîtra."
          }
        },
        "hi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "माइग्रेशन पूरा हुआ। क्या आप %lld माइग्रेट किए गए ऐप्स को Ad-hoc पुनः हस्ताक्षर करना चाहेंगे?\n\nहस्ताक्षर के बाद, ऐप्स सामान्य रूप से लॉन्च हो सकते हैं और Finder की \"क्षतिग्रस्त\" चेतावनी गायब हो जाएगी।"
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migration complete. Would you like to Ad-hoc resign the %lld migrated apps?\n\nAfter resigning, apps can launch normally and the Finder \"damaged\" warning will disappear."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migrazione completata. Vuoi firmare le %lld app migrate in Ad-hoc?\n\nDopo la firma, le app possono essere avviate normalmente e l'avviso \"danneggiato\" di Finder scomparirà."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migration complete. Would you like to Ad-hoc resign the %lld migrated apps?\n\nAfter resigning, apps can launch normally and the Finder \"damaged\" warning will disappear."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "마이그레이션이 완료되었습니다. 마이그레이션된 %lld개 앱에 Ad-hoc 서명을 하시겠습니까?\n\n서명 후 앱이 정상적으로 실행되며 Finder의 \"손상됨\" 경고가 사라집니다."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migratie voltooid. Wilt u de %lld gemigreerde apps Ad-hoc opnieuw ondertekenen?\n\nNa ondertekening kunnen apps normaal worden gestart en verdwijnt de Finder-melding \"beschadigd\"."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migracja zakończone. Czy chcesz podpisać %lld zmigrowanych aplikacji Ad-hoc?\n\nPo podpisaniu aplikacje mogą się normalnie uruchamiać, a ostrzeżenie Findera \"uszkodzone\" zniknie."
          }
        },
        "pt" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Migração concluída. Deseja re-assinar os %lld apps migrados em Ad-hoc?\n\nApós a assinatura, os apps podem ser iniciados normalmente e o aviso \"danificado\" do Finder desaparecerá."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Миграция завершена. Хотите переподписать %lld мигрированных приложений Ad-hoc?\n\nПосле подписи приложения будут запускаться нормально, а предупреждение Finder \"повреждено\" исчезнет."
          }
        },
        "th" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "การย้ายเสร็จสิ้น ต้องการเซ็น %lld แอปที่ย้ายแล้วแบบ Ad-hoc หรือไม่?\n\nหลังเซ็น แอปจะเปิดใช้งานได้ตามปกติ และคำเตือน \"เสียหาย\" ของ Finder จะหายไป"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Taşıma tamamlandı. Taşınan %lld uygulamayı Ad-hoc yeniden imzalamak ister misiniz?\n\nİmzalama sonrası uygulamalar normal şekilde başlatılabilir ve Finder \"hasarlı\" uyarısı kaybolur."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Di chuyển hoàn tất. Bạn có muốn ký lại %lld ứng dụng đã di chuyển bằng Ad-hoc không?\n\nSau khi ký, ứng dụng có thể khởi động bình thường và cảnh báo \"bị hỏng\" của Finder sẽ biến mất."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "迁移完成。是否对已迁移的 %lld 个应用进行 Ad-hoc 重签名？\\n\\n重签名后应用可在本地正常启动，Finder「已损坏」提示将消失。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "遷移完成。是否對已遷移的 %lld 個應用進行 Ad-hoc 重簽名？\n\n重簽名後應用可在本地正常啟動，Finder「已損壞」提示將消失。"
          }
        },
        "zh-martian" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "遷迻宪成。昰否怼已遷迻の %lld 個應詠進行 Ad-hoc 重簽銘？\n\n重簽銘後應詠可在夲地怔憲啟憟，Finder「已損壞」提⽰將消失。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "迁移完成后，原路径将自动变成符号链接，相关工具无需任何修改即可继续使用。" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "After migration, the original path will automatically become a symbolic link, and related tools can continue to be used without any modification."
          }
        },
        "br" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
